 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $k_{0}:=\tilde{h}-P_{\mathcal{G}}\tilde{h}$
\end_inset

 and note that by linearity
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\Gamma\left(k_{0}\right) & =\Gamma\left(\tilde{h}\right)-\Gamma\left(P_{\mathcal{G}}\tilde{h}\right)\\
 & =1
\end{align*}

