\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\innerproduct{k_{0}}h=\Gamma\left(h\right)\pnorm{k_{0}}{}^{2}.
\]

\end_inset

Recall that 
\begin_inset Formula $\pnorm{k_{0}}{}>0$
\end_inset

