\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
0 & =\innerproduct h{k_{1}}-\innerproduct h{k_{2}}\\
 & =\innerproduct h{k_{1}-k_{2}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

for any 
\begin_inset Formula $h\in\mathcal{H}.$
