 In particular, this holds 
\begin_inset Formula $h=k_{1}-k_{2}$
\end_inset

 in which case
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\pnorm{k_{1}-k_{2}}{}^{2}=0\implies k_{1}=k_{2}
\]

\end_inset

completing the proof.
